---
import ZhLayout from '../../layouts/ZhLayout.astro';
---

<ZhLayout
  title="DGSDK | 静电消除器与工业清洁机制造商"
  description="东莞史帝克自动化设备有限公司，专业生产静电消除器、工业清洁机、自动化设备和精密CNC零件。服务全球工业客户。"
  canonical="https://www.dg-sdk.com/zh/"
  image="/assets/img/header-bg.webp"
>

  <!-- 结构化数据 -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": ["Organization", "LocalBusiness"],
    "name": "DGSDK",
    "alternateName": "东莞史帝克自动化设备有限公司",
    "url": "https://www.dg-sdk.com",
    "logo": { "@type": "ImageObject", "url": "https://www.dg-sdk.com/logo.png", "width": 600, "height": 168 },
    "image": "https://www.dg-sdk.com/assets/img/header-bg.webp",
    "description": "专业制造商，专注于静电消除系统、工业清洁机、自动化设备和精密CNC零件。",
    "foundingDate": "2013",
    "address": { "@type": "PostalAddress", "streetAddress": "滨海路33号", "addressLocality": "东莞", "addressRegion": "广东", "postalCode": "523000", "addressCountry": "CN" },
    "contactPoint": { "@type": "ContactPoint", "telephone": "+86-13602342003", "contactType": "sales", "availableLanguage": ["English", "Chinese"], "areaServed": "Worldwide" }
  }
  </script>

  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- HERO 第一屏 -->
    <section class="parallax-hero parallax-hero-1">
      <div class="parallax-overlay"></div>
      <div class="container parallax-content" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="900">
        <p class="parallax-sub">东莞史帝克自动化设备有限公司</p>
        <h1 class="parallax-heading">静电消除器 · 清洁机 · CNC制造</h1>
        <p class="parallax-desc">为电子、SMT、光学薄膜、自动化设备和精密制造提供专业工业解决方案。</p>
        <a class="parallax-btn" href="/zh/contact">获取报价</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 核心产品 -->
    <section class="page-section" id="services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
          <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">核心产品</h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">先进的工业解决方案，提高效率、减少缺陷、优化生产流程。</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center">
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
            <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator" class="product-card">
              <span class="fa-stack fa-4x product-icon"><i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i><i class="fas fa-bolt fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i></span>
              <h4>静电消除系统</h4>
              <p>高性能离子设备，消除静电，提高生产稳定性，适用于电子、SMT及包装生产线。</p>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <a href="/zh/products/automation" class="product-card">
              <span class="fa-stack fa-4x product-icon"><i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i><i class="fas fa-gears fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i></span>
              <h4>自动化系统</h4>
              <p>定制自动化解决方案，简化工作流程，提高生产效率，降低人工操作成本。</p>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts" class="product-card">
              <span class="fa-stack fa-4x product-icon"><i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i><i class="fas fa-industry fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i></span>
              <h4>精密CNC零件</h4>
              <p>严格质量控制的高精度CNC加工，稳定公差，性能可靠，支持OEM定制。</p>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
            <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine" class="product-card">
              <span class="fa-stack fa-4x product-icon"><i class="fas fa-circle fa-stack-2x text-primary"></i><i class="fas fa-soap fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i></span>
              <h4>工业清洁机</h4>
              <p>适用于PCB、FPC、SMT、偏光片、背光板和光学薄膜制造的精密清洁设备。</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-4" data-aos="fade-up">
          <a href="/zh/products" class="btn btn-warning text-uppercase px-4 py-2">查看所有产品</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 视差横幅 2 -->
    <section class="parallax-hero parallax-hero-2">
      <div class="parallax-overlay"></div>
      <div class="container parallax-content" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-duration="800">
        <p class="parallax-label">我们的制造实力</p>
        <h2 class="parallax-banner-text">精密.<br/>可靠.<br/>创新.</h2>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 应用领域 -->
    <section class="page-section bg-light" id="portfolio">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
          <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">应用领域</h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">了解我们的解决方案如何提高效率、减少缺陷、优化生产线。</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
            <a href="/zh/applications" class="portfolio-item app-card">
              <div class="portfolio-link">
                <picture>
                  <source srcset="/assets/img/portfolio/1-700.webp 700w, /assets/img/portfolio/1.webp 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 679px" type="image/webp" />
                  <picture><source srcset="/assets/img/portfolio/1.webp" type="image/webp" /><img class="img-fluid" src="/assets/img/portfolio/1.jpg" alt="电子制造" loading="lazy" width="679" height="509" /></picture>
                </picture>
              </div>
              <div class="portfolio-caption">
                <div class="portfolio-caption-heading">电子制造</div>
                <div class="portfolio-caption-subheading text-muted">静电控制与清洁解决方案</div>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
            <a href="/zh/applications" class="portfolio-item app-card">
              <div class="portfolio-link">
                <picture>
                  <source srcset="/assets/img/portfolio/2-700.webp 700w, /assets/img/portfolio/2-900.webp 900w, /assets/img/portfolio/2.webp 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 679px" type="image/webp" />
                  <picture><source srcset="/assets/img/portfolio/2.webp" type="image/webp" /><img class="img-fluid" src="/assets/img/portfolio/2.jpg" alt="SMT生产" loading="lazy" width="679" height="509" /></picture>
                </picture>
              </div>
              <div class="portfolio-caption">
                <div class="portfolio-caption-heading">SMT生产</div>
                <div class="portfolio-caption-subheading text-muted">工业自动化与设备支持</div>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
            <a href="/zh/applications" class="portfolio-item app-card">
              <div class="portfolio-link">
                <picture>
                  <source srcset="/assets/img/portfolio/3-700.webp 700w, /assets/img/portfolio/3.webp 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 679px" type="image/webp" />
                  <picture><source srcset="/assets/img/portfolio/3.webp" type="image/webp" /><img class="img-fluid" src="/assets/img/portfolio/3.jpg" alt="精密加工" loading="lazy" width="679" height="509" /></picture>
                </picture>
              </div>
              <div class="portfolio-caption">
                <div class="portfolio-caption-heading">精密加工</div>
                <div class="portfolio-caption-subheading text-muted">高精度CNC零件解决方案</div>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-4" data-aos="fade-up">
          <a href="/zh/contact" class="btn btn-warning text-uppercase px-4 py-2">讨论您的应用需求</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 视差横幅 3 -->
    <section class="parallax-hero parallax-hero-3">
      <div class="parallax-overlay"></div>
      <div class="container parallax-content" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="800">
        <p class="parallax-label">始于2013年</p>
        <h2 class="parallax-banner-text">制造于<br/>东莞.</h2>
        <p class="parallax-desc" style="max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 28px;">十余年静电控制、精密加工和工业自动化制造经验。</p>
        <a class="parallax-btn" href="/zh/about">了解我们</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 关于我们 -->
    <section class="page-section" id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
          <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">关于史帝克</h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">东莞史帝克自动化设备有限公司</h3>
        </div>
        <ul class="timeline">
          <li data-aos="fade-right">
            <div class="timeline-image"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/about/1.webp" type="image/webp" /><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="/assets/img/about/1.jpg" alt="公司成立" loading="lazy" /></picture></div>
            <div class="timeline-panel">
              <div class="timeline-heading"><h4>2013年成立</h4><h4 class="subheading">专业工业制造商</h4></div>
              <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">史帝克成立于东莞，专注于工业自动化、静电消除系统和精密制造解决方案，服务全球客户。</p></div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="timeline-inverted" data-aos="fade-left">
            <div class="timeline-image"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/about/2.webp" type="image/webp" /><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="/assets/img/about/2.jpg" alt="技术发展" loading="lazy" /></picture></div>
            <div class="timeline-panel">
              <div class="timeline-heading"><h4>技术扩展</h4><h4 class="subheading">静电控制与清洁解决方案</h4></div>
              <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">我们扩展了产品范围，包括适用于电子、SMT和光学薄膜行业的静电消除器和工业清洁机。</p></div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li data-aos="fade-right">
            <div class="timeline-image"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/about/3.webp" type="image/webp" /><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="/assets/img/about/3.jpg" alt="先进制造" loading="lazy" /></picture></div>
            <div class="timeline-panel">
              <div class="timeline-heading"><h4>制造能力提升</h4><h4 class="subheading">自动化、静电控制、CNC</h4></div>
              <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">我们的核心业务现涵盖自动化系统、静电控制设备、清洁机、精密CNC零件和OEM制造服务。</p></div>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="timeline-inverted" data-aos="fade-left">
            <div class="timeline-image"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/about/4.webp" type="image/webp" /><img class="rounded-circle img-fluid" src="/assets/img/about/4.jpg" alt="全球服务" loading="lazy" /></picture></div>
            <div class="timeline-panel">
              <div class="timeline-heading"><h4>全球服务</h4><h4 class="subheading">长期工业合作</h4></div>
              <div class="timeline-body"><p class="text-muted">史帝克以稳定的产品质量、工程支持和实用的工业解决方案为全球客户提供长期合作服务。</p></div>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 资质认证 -->
    <section id="certifications" class="page-section bg-light">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
          <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">资质认证</h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">认证质量与国际合规</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="cert-grid">
          <div class="cert-card" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="0"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/cert/cert1.webp" type="image/webp" /><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert1.png" alt="证书1" loading="lazy" width="300" height="212" /></picture></div>
          <div class="cert-card" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="60"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/cert/cert2.webp" type="image/webp" /><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert2.png" alt="证书2" loading="lazy" width="300" height="212" /></picture></div>
          <div class="cert-card" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="120"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/cert/cert3.webp" type="image/webp" /><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert3.png" alt="证书3" loading="lazy" width="300" height="212" /></picture></div>
          <div class="cert-card" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="180"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/cert/cert4.webp" type="image/webp" /><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert4.png" alt="证书4" loading="lazy" width="300" height="212" /></picture></div>
          <div class="cert-card" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="240"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/cert/cert5.webp" type="image/webp" /><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert5.png" alt="证书5" loading="lazy" width="300" height="212" /></picture></div>
          <div class="cert-card" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="300"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/cert/cert6.webp" type="image/webp" /><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert6.png" alt="证书6" loading="lazy" width="300" height="212" /></picture></div>
          <div class="cert-card" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="360"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/cert/cert7.webp" type="image/webp" /><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert7.png" alt="证书7" loading="lazy" width="300" height="212" /></picture></div>
          <div class="cert-card" data-aos="zoom-in" data-aos-delay="420"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/cert/cert8.webp" type="image/webp" /><img src="/assets/img/cert/cert8.png" alt="证书8" loading="lazy" width="300" height="212" /></picture></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 技术博客预览 -->
    <section class="page-section" style="background:#f5f6f7;padding:70px 20px;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:40px;" data-aos="fade-up">
          <h2 class="section-heading text-uppercase">技术博客</h2>
          <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">工业清洁机和自动化设备的操作指南与行业技术资讯。</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-index-grid" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <a href="/zh/blog/polarizer-cleaner-tutorial" class="blog-index-card">
            <div class="blog-index-img"><picture><source srcset="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner.webp" type="image/webp" /><img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner.jpg" alt="偏光片清洁机操作教程" loading="lazy" /></picture></div>
            <div class="blog-index-content">
              <div class="blog-index-tags"><span class="blog-tag">清洁机</span><span class="blog-tag">操作教程</span></div>
              <h2>偏光片清洁机操作指南：8步实现零缺陷清洁效果</h2>
              <p>逐步学习偏光片清洁机的操作方法——参数设置、耗材安装、故障排除，以及如何实现99%以上清洁良率。</p>
              <div class="blog-index-meta">
                <span><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> 2026年5月13日</span>
                <span><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> 约10分钟</span>
              </div>
              <span class="blog-read-more">阅读全文 <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:32px;" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150">
          <a href="/zh/blog" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;border-radius:10px;background:#111827;color:#fff;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;">查看全部文章</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 获取报价 -->
    <section class="quote-section" id="contact">
      <div class="quote-overlay"></div>
      <div class="container quote-content">
        <div class="text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
          <h2 class="quote-title">获取免费报价</h2>
          <p class="quote-desc">如果您需要了解我们的产品，请填写以下表格提交询价，工作日24小时内回复。</p>
        </div>
        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mvzlpdwy" method="POST" class="quote-form" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="您的姓名（必填）" required />
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="您的电子邮箱（必填）" required />
          <input type="text" name="phone" placeholder="您的电话号码" />
          <textarea name="message" rows="5" placeholder="请输入您的询价内容" required></textarea>
          <input type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display:none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
          <button type="submit">发送询价</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <!-- 底部 CTA -->
  <section class="home-bottom-cta">
    <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
      <h2>准备好开始您的项目了吗？</h2>
      <p>联系史帝克，获取工业自动化、静电消除器、清洁机和精密CNC零件的专业解决方案。</p>
      <a href="/zh/contact" class="home-bottom-btn">获取免费报价</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</ZhLayout>
